dct_description_sm: Verso: Lehigh Valley, Pennsylvania, and Philadelphia area (1:181,028), and high oblique air photograph of Philadelphia. Title on verso: Cushman & Wakefield in Pennsylvania, Philadelphia. Shows residential, office and other governmental, institutional, and commercial buildings, as well as parks and proposed developments in downtown area. Text, high oblique air photograph, and metropolitan region road map on verso.
